Cape Town Mayor Geordin Hill-Lewis is about to brief the media to thank the firefighters who helped to contain the fire at Parliament. The fire broke out on Sunday and caused extensive damage to the old and new National Assembly buildings. National Assembly Speaker Nosiviwe Mapisa-Nqakula and Western Cape Premier Alan Winde are also at the briefing. LIVE:
